*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form get_emp_name
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&      --> ZSSA0073_PERNR
*&      <-- ZSSA0073_ENAME
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM get_emp_name  USING    VALUE(p_pernr)
                   CHANGING VALUE(p_ename).


  CALL FUNCTION 'ZFSA07_01'
    EXPORTING
      iv_pernr = p_pernr
    IMPORTING
      ev_ename = p_ename.

ENDFORM.


